ck sqs-block-html\" data-block-type=\"2\" data-border-radii=\"&#123;&quot;topLeft&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;,&quot;topRight&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;,&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;,&quot;bottomRight&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;&#125;\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" id=\"block-yui_3_17_2_1_1692623751407_86555\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n\n<div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content>\n  <p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Friday, July 11th!  Friday Night Retro Dance Party with DJ Don Black!</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Resident DJ Don Black typically plays the last Friday of the month.<br>Don Black is bringing the heat and all his favorite retro songs for this Friday Night Retro Dance Party.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Don plays everything from the 80s and 90s, including dance, disco, funk, and alternative. The first two hours are all requests.<br>You read that right:</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">THE FIRST TWO HOURS ARE ALL REQUESTS!</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Make sure to get here when the doors open at 9 PM to get your requests in!</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Doors @ 9pm Cover $7. 21+</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n\n</div></div></div></div></div>",
